CISCO IOS CONFIGURATION OSPFv3

Router01
configure terminal
ipv6 unicast-routing
ipv6 router ospf 1
router-id 10.0.0.1
passive-interface loopback 0
passive-interface Gi0/7
interface gi0/1
ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
ipv6 ospf cost 10
interface loopback 0 
ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
ipv6 ospf cost 10
interface gi0/7
ipv6 ospf 1 area 0.0.0.0
ipv6 ospf cost 10


